{"tid":1666550,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[非自駕] Tasmania local tour 邊間好?","createTime":"2019-10-21T04:34:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T10:19:01.000Z","uid":165840,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b38fb6ae2d60093f733f6ab93e60d58befeb0e74","tid":1666550,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T04:34:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />11月尾出發 大約會有7日 full day黎join local tour, 有冇巴打分享下7日夠唔夠玩?<br />\n同埋有無邊間信譽唔錯無伏?<br />\n<br />\n暫時上網睇左呢間 jump tour, 7日要成AUD 950, 唔知算平定貴?<br />\n<a href=\"https://jumptours.com.au/best-tasmania-tour/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjumptours.com.au%2Fbest-tasmania-tour%2F&d=IZFSAkWTwbXSesVVmoeERebr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=e61b4ed3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://jumptours.com.au/best-tasmania-tour/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12d37f22a8fde70f60e7b3cb775f0abd348f0ed7","tid":1666550,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T04:35:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb3a1c7376ab385f1390ed0cf1f9856d5890a8ed","tid":1666550,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T04:37:05.000Z","msg":"不如全港黨鐵靜坐聲討721啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1665580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1665580</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27a77c03c36d758e3c136ff50a2ad864f8d51998","tid":1666550,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb3a1c7376ab385f1390e