5(6005唔需要特登買，成本價貴)+5n11/5p71(唔建議5p71,如果要嘅不如買502再搭P100綿抵啲)+501蓋<br />\n例如：6200+6001CN+5n11+501 我見100已經有一set<br />\n而且 就算唔用5n11同501蓋 都ok 6001CN一對最平$30，我見$50通常都有<br />\n6003貴少少 $70成平價(睇你有冇運見到)<br />\n以上都可以頂到TG，但記得聞到味要即換<br />\n<br />\n想了解更多快啲入去連登睇啦😛<br />\n...<br />\n防毒面具篇完<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1666931\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1666931</a>"},{"pid":"1b73ce09ffc513d104170dc9ddeaf91a719bc415","tid":1666550,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:03:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a23ad5a2c3a2800b711f2dcd2f90d6638b1226d","tid":1666550,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:59:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c344d7a4987c796d954b6cfd3051328ed57abe1","tid":1666550,"uid":68132,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:02:49.000Z","msg":"我前年應該都係玩呢個tour<br />\n個guide都幾玩得"},{"pid":"e6e6c47f94981aaf0b0c8c32a9d6ef74c38bd934","tid":1666550,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c344d7a4987c796d954b6cfd3051328ed57abe1","tid":1666550,"uid":68132,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:02:49.000Z","msg":"我前年應該都係玩呢個tour<br />\n個guide都幾玩得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T12:03:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都係jump tour? 可以分享多d嗎 行程 團友有無伏 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f55b0a72c5cf063de55a170e02137ccbf47d604","tid":1666550,"uid":68132,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e6e6c47f94981aaf0b0c8c32a9d6ef74c38bd934","tid":1666550,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c344d7a4987c796d954b6cfd3051328ed57abe1","tid":1666550,"uid":68132,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:02:49.000Z","msg":"我前年應該都係玩呢個tour<br />\n個guide都幾玩得"},"